This thread continuously updates the graph when it changes.
The graph gets updated in one of two ways:
1: The structure of the SMACH plans has changed, or the display settings have been changed. In this case, the dotcode needs to be regenerated.
2: The status of the SMACH plans has changed. In this case, we only need to change the styles of the graph.
